item.description:
Chief Celia Hyde, the President of the Massachusetts chapter of Oath Keepers and a member of its national board will be the feaure speaker at our luncheon.

She will discuss the history of Oath Keppers, its goal and mission.

Celia Hyde was a Massachusetts police officer and spend six years as the police chief of Bolton, MA. Since, 2005 she has been running the Stowaway Bed andBreakfast in Stow, MA.

Price includes a hearty lunch. Fish $22, Chicken $20 RSVPs are required.
